// grid arrange all clips greedily

/*
NoIndex: true
Description: grid arrange all clips greedily
About: 
  This is a video arrangement script that:
    * split screen in to N x M configurable small blocks up to 16x16
    * find largest n x m spot for each track with configurable restrictions
    * search of next clip position is roughly done by Euclidean distance to
      either "center" or left/top on corresponding dimension 
    * Blurs the first encountered clip as background. (code copied from Reaper)
Version: 0.1
Author: tdihp
*/

